{"tid":1251371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Johnny喜多川傳病危","createTime":"2019-06-22T13:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T15:44:32.000Z","uid":3873,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e7ac452ebba1373f154822d7038a64d488e9f81","tid":1251371,"uid":3873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190620/59740186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59740186&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3pmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b6286ef0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190620%2F59740186&h=918058cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190620/59740186</a><br />\n<br />\n日本尊尼事務所的87歲創辦人Johnny喜多川，星期二傳出入院消息，報道指他在位於東京澀谷的寓所倒下，家中有人致電報警後將他送院。<br />\n<br />\n消息連日來引起媒體注意，醫院外聚集許多記者，由於尊尼事務所至今並未對外說明病情，導致外界流傳「重病說」。<br />\n<br />\nJohnny喜多川入院消息眾說紛紜，《Friday》網上版指中居正廣與瀧澤秀明前日各自抵達醫院，而KinKi Kids、V6、TOKIO、KAT-TUN均有成員在昨日趕到醫院，有指公司會在下星期才向外公佈有關Johnny喜多川的消息。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n但岩岩睇twitter又有人傳佢死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.2nn.jp/newsplus/1561206170/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.2nn.jp%2Fnewsplus%2F1561206170%2F&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3pmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=ec168fd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.2nn.jp/newsplus/1561206170/</a><br />\nジャニーズ事務所の代表取締役社長であり、芸能プロモーターでもあるジャニー喜多川社長(87歳)が亡くなったことがわかった。ジャニー喜多川社長は以前から体調が芳しくなく、健康状態が心配されていた。・ジャニーズタレントが病院に集結<br />\n2019年6月18日(木曜日)正午過ぎ、ジャニー喜多川社長が体調を著しく崩し、都内の病院へ緊急搬送された。"},{"pid":"fa245653d89655030130eda3feaa995df7dbfda1","tid":1251371,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"Fake news"}]}